1. *Divna* voda je tekla po potoku. (Beautiful water was flowing down the stream.)
2. Ona je nacrtala *divnu* sliku. (She drew a beautiful picture.)
3. Njena *divna* devojčica je bila pametna. (Her beautiful daughter was smart.)
4. *Divnim* osećanjima počastvovana je. (She was honored by wonderful feelings.)
5. Ova *divna* priroda je neprocenjiva. (This beautiful nature is priceless.)